---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import LeadCapturePanel from '../components/LeadCapturePanel.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Policies" description="Dazzle policy overview for custom orders, certification, shipping, exchange, resizing, care, and consultation-led laboratory-grown diamond jewellery purchases.">
  <section class="container page-section">
    <h1>Dazzle Policies</h1>
    <p class="large-text">These policy notes are written to help buyers understand the consultation-first process. Final order terms should be confirmed in writing before payment.</p>
    <h2>Custom and made-to-order pieces</h2>
    <p>Many laboratory-grown diamond pieces are made after design, metal, stone, and budget confirmation. Timelines depend on design complexity, certification availability, and metal work.</p>
    <h2>Certification and disclosure</h2>
    <p>Dazzle should disclose laboratory-grown diamond origin clearly and provide certificate details for eligible high-value pieces before confirmation.</p>
    <h2>Gold hallmarking</h2>
    <p>Gold jewellery should be discussed with BIS hallmarking and metal purity clarity. Ask for final metal details in the quote.</p>
    <h2>Shipping and insurance</h2>
    <p>Shipping route, insurance, identity verification, and handover process depend on product value and destination. Confirm these before dispatch.</p>
    <h2>Exchange, resizing, and returns</h2>
    <p>Custom pieces, engraved pieces, resized rings, and special-order stones may have limited returns. Confirm exchange and resizing terms before payment.</p>
  </section>
  <section class="container"><LeadCapturePanel title="Clarify policy terms before ordering" /></section>
</BaseLayout>
